    },
    "amorphous": {
      "// note": "Incorporeal / ooze (wraith, grimeling) — a core essence + outer mass, no skeleton. The outer mass lashes out: it enables both the wraith's spectral_strike AND a physical claw/pseudopod (a creature only uses the weapons IT lists — the wraith strikes spectrally, the grimeling claws).",
      "parts": {
